    "description": "<p>Only a <strong>dwarf</strong>, <strong>halfling</strong>, <strong>fighter</strong>, <strong>thief</strong>, or <strong>mystic</strong> may use this unusual item. It may be used as a spear +3 in all respects. On command of the user, it will stop wherever it is, and it cannot be moved by any means except a wish. A second command releases it. If the item is in motion when stopped, it will continue its direction when released. For example, it may be thrown toward a door and commanded to stop, later released if an enemy enters so that it will continue toward the enemy (a normal attack roll is made). If the user falls, a command will stop it suddenly, and the user may hold on to it.</p>",
